[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ふう……あのヘルトさんたちと会うと、\nいっつも疲れちゃいます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01470",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ずっと気を張ることになるからね。\nそれこそ気を抜いたら圧倒されてしまう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01471",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あ、変てこ仮面さん……皆さんは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01472",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "みんなとっとと解散しちゃったよ？\n嬢ちゃんのボスも手続きで本部に行ったみたいだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01473",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "大変です！　ボスを手伝わなきゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01474",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おっと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01475",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "悪いことは言わないから、もうちょっと休んだら？\n夜の海に落っこちたら大変だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01476",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "どっちが上か分からないから、潜ってるのか\n水面に向かってるのか分からなくなるんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01477",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "なんだか不思議なお話ですね。\n……分かりました、少し休みます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01478",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "それで……放してもらえますか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01479",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おっと、こりゃ失礼",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01480",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "意外でした。変てこ仮面さんがボスの誘いに乗ったの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01481",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、エルスも驚いていたね。\nそんなに意外かい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01482",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "変てこ仮面さんはいつも上手く立ち回って\n自分は危険な目にあわず手柄を奪ってくじゃないですか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01483",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺、そんな風に思われてたのか……けど、そうだね。\nこの稼業は身体が資本、なるべく危険は冒さない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01484",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "それなのに、なんで今回は体を張って\n一緒に九偉人を止める気になったんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01485",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "答えは簡単、あの九偉人ってのがおっかないからさ。\n人類を「管理」する上位存在なんざ出てきたら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01486",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "賞金首はもちろん、賞金稼ぎである俺だって\n「管理」対象にされちゃう。おまんま食い上げだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01487",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "なるほど……自分の都合なんですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01488",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……逆に聞くけど、嬢ちゃんはなんで\n九偉人とかいう馬の骨とやり合おうとしてるのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01489",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "他人のためとか、怖いボスの言いなりだからとかなら\n無理にやらなくてもいいんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01490",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "今のは聞き捨てなりません、訂正してください。ボスは\n確かに怖いですけど、そんな人でなしじゃありません",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01491",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "誰に強制されたわけでもなく、私が自分で考えて……\n自分の意思で戦おうって決めたんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01492",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうか、悪かった。訂正するよ。\nでもさ、まだ緊張で顔が強張ってるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01493",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そんなんで雷鳴の島に行ったら、\n雷の音にたまげて転んだりしちゃうんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01494",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "むぅ……またそうやって茶化す！\n変てこ仮面さんのそういうところ、嫌いです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01495",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうか、嫌われちゃったか。悲しいね、こりゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01496",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "でも、そうやって場を和ませようとするところ……\nお兄ちゃんに似てて、思い出しちゃいます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01497",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……その、お兄ちゃんって？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01498",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "故郷のヌルスラで、面倒を見てくれた\n近所のお兄ちゃんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01499",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "お兄ちゃんはいつも私のことを見て、\n優しくしてくれました……でも……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01500",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01501",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "お兄ちゃんはある日突然、いなくなりました。\n私をかばって人攫いに攫われたんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01502",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ヌルスラの評判は知っている。嬢ちゃんには悪いけど\nその兄ちゃんが生きている可能性は低いと思うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01503",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい……でも、私は信じてるんです。\nお兄ちゃんは生きてるって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01504",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "監察官になって当時のことを調べました。\n当時ヌルスラで暗躍していた人攫い……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01505",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "それを主導していたのは異端の教団。\nその教団はある日、突然謎の壊滅を遂げた……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01506",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "攫われた兄ちゃんは、その壊滅のどさくさに\n紛れてどこかに逃げ延びている……と？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01507",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい……私はそう信じています。だから監察官として\n色んな島に行くたびに、こっそり探してるんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01508",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "また「ギヨームお兄ちゃん」に会いたい……\nそれが私の夢なんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01509",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "でもあの九偉人が「管理」を始めたら、監察官も\nみんなクビになって、私の夢が果たせませんからね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01510",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……そんなに愛されてるとは。\nギヨームお兄ちゃんに妬けちゃうね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01511",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "一番初め貴方に会った時ギヨームお兄ちゃんかと思って\n聞いてしまったんですよ。覚えてないでしょうけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01512",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうだったっけ。そんなに似てる感じだったのか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01513",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "これ、秘密にしてくださいね？\nここまで詳しいことはボスにしか言ってないんですから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01514",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、俺の胸のうちにそっとしまっておくさ。\n宝物を扱うみたいにね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01515",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "変てこ仮面さん、たまにそうやって\n気持ち悪い言い回ししますよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01516",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……浪漫のある言い回しと言ってほしいね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01517",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
